Class ProblemInput

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.faylixe.googlecodejam.client.common.NamedObject
      • fr.faylixe.googlecodejam.client.webservice.ProblemInput
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class ProblemInput
extends NamedObject
implements Serializable

    POJO that aims to be bind to the /ContestInfo request, using Gson API. ProblemInput instance belong to a Problem object, and describes input submission available for a given Problem.
